✅NOTES HOW TO START FROM DOCKER
myadmin@kdcio:~/toha-gamma/my-portfolio$ docker run --rm -p 1313:1313   -v /home/myadmin/toha-gamma/my-portfolio:/src   -w /src   klakegg/hugo:ext-debian   server -D --disableFastRender --bind 0.0.0.0 --baseURL http://207.148.0.99:1313

WHERE TO GET TAGS: https://hub.docker.com/r/klakegg/hugo


✅NOTES STARTING FROM AN INSTALLATION ON VULTR SYSTEM - CLEAN SYSTEM BEFORE STARTING:
myadmin@kdcio:~/toha-gamma/my-portfolio$ rm -rf resources/  public/
myadmin@kdcio:~/toha-gamma/my-portfolio$ hugo mod clean
myadmin@kdcio:~/toha-gamma/my-portfolio$ hugo server -D --disableFastRender --cleanDestinationDir -p 1313 --bind 0.0.0.0 --baseURL http://207.148.0.99:1313


hugo server -D --disableFastRender --cleanDestinationDir -p 1313 --bind 0.0.0.0 --baseURL http://207.148.0.99:1313


